{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-news-post-js","path":"/news/recruitment","result":{"data":{"contentfulNews":{"id":"0656009a-713f-5139-822f-14fefd307340","title":"We're Growing! Join our executive team.","slug":"recruitment","article":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Hi All!</p>\n<p>UTM Robotics is hiring for this upcoming 2021-2022 school year, to aid in involving the MCS community in robotics. Join us in our journey to build an engaging community partaking in educational and competitive events focused around simulation robotics. </p>\n<p>We are looking to hire technical officers, marketing officers, as well as logistics officers. All returning students are welcome to apply!</p>\n<p>More details can be found on our linktree: <a href=\"https://linktr.ee/utmrobotics\">https://linktr.ee/utmrobotics</a></p>\n<p>Applications are due by Sunday, July 11th. We're looking forward to meeting you!</p>"}},"featureImage":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/hyhmgfckc4j9/1eaqlMQ1fVvSBf5f2kkK1X/0078345000ee69fc0832838e7b38f495/RoboticsHiringPosterDiscord.png?w=1500&q=50","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/hyhmgfckc4j9/1eaqlMQ1fVvSBf5f2kkK1X/0078345000ee69fc0832838e7b38f495/RoboticsHiringPosterDiscord.png?w=375&h=375&q=50 375w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/hyhmgfckc4j9/1eaqlMQ1fVvSBf5f2kkK1X/0078345000ee69fc0832838e7b38f495/RoboticsHiringPosterDiscord.png?w=750&h=750&q=50 750w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/hyhmgfckc4j9/1eaqlMQ1fVvSBf5f2kkK1X/0078345000ee69fc0832838e7b38f495/RoboticsHiringPosterDiscord.png?w=1080&h=1080&q=50 1080w","srcWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/hyhmgfckc4j9/1eaqlMQ1fVvSBf5f2kkK1X/0078345000ee69fc0832838e7b38f495/RoboticsHiringPosterDiscord.png?w=1500&q=50&fm=webp","srcSetWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/hyhmgfckc4j9/1eaqlMQ1fVvSBf5f2kkK1X/0078345000ee69fc0832838e7b38f495/RoboticsHiringPosterDiscord.png?w=375&h=375&q=50&fm=webp 375w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/hyhmgfckc4j9/1eaqlMQ1fVvSBf5f2kkK1X/0078345000ee69